title: Feldherr 3 pcs. Value Pack Storage Box 7 Slots for N Scale - Lying Compatible with Model Railway locomotives, Wagons and Vehicles
features: Three fully-equipped Feldherr Storage Boxes with 21 slots total for model railways in N Gauge. For protected storage and transport of your trains and wagons.

The Full-Size foam trays are divided into 7 compartments each, tailor-made for model trains in Gauge N, in lying position. Each of the compartments is 329 mm long x 30 mm wide x 25 mm deep. Several trains and carriages can be stored next to each other in one compartment. Spacers for separation are available (HS025A001).
The models are safely stored all around and are reliably and permanently protected against damage and wear and tear such as scratches and flaking paint by the high-quality foam.
Fine pored quality foam - Made in Germany - acid-free - chlorine-free
